No. D-2483. In the Matter of Discipline of Donald F. Mintmire. 561 U.S. 1044, 131 S. Ct. 42,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1131,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5613. July 26, 2010.

Donald F. Mintmire, of Palm Beach, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
